        <Parent_String>ball striking or snaring and throwing equipment [300217891], ball game equipment [300211062], sports and athletic equipment [300211035], recreational artifacts (equipment) [300218781], Recreational Artifacts (hierarchy name) [300136012], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
